<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">{schemaJsons.map((schema) => (<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />))}</Fragment>
  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>Miele MasterCool service? Same-day across all 5 SoCal counties:</span><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a></div></div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › <a href="/brands/miele/">Miele</a> › Built-In Refrigerator Repair</div>
    <h1>Miele Built-In Refrigerator Repair</h1>
    <p class="lede">Miele is the German family-owned luxury appliance manufacturer based in Gütersloh since 1899 — now 4th-generation Miele and Zinkann family ownership, with engineering continuity across 125+ years of product development. MasterCool is Miele's luxury built-in refrigerator line: integrated column architecture with F1411Vi + F2811Vi freezer columns, K1911Vi + K2902Vi refrigerator columns, KF 2981 Vi combination refrigerator-freezer, and legacy KFN 9855 iDE French-door built-ins still in active LA service. Panel-ready full-overlay integration is the MasterCool signature — these units install flush with custom cabinetry for European design-direction kitchens in Beverly Hills, Brentwood, West Hollywood, Silver Lake, and Pacific Palisades design-forward remodels. Miele announced a new Leeds, Alabama manufacturing plant in 2023 coming online 2025 — first US plant, expanding parts availability over time. <b>Important:</b> this page covers Miele residential only — Miele Professional (commercial foodservice / laundry / laboratory) is a separate product line with separate service network. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
