      <li><b>Gütersloh Germany 1899 family</b> — 4th generation Miele + Zinkann</li>
      <li><b>Alabama 2025 plant</b> — first US Miele manufacturing facility</li>
      <li><b>$89 residential diagnostic</b> — waived when you authorize the repair</li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />

  <section class="trust-bar"><div class="wrap"><span>CSLB #1138898 · Insured</span><span>Same-day in 5 SoCal counties</span><span>Residential diagnostic $89 · waived with repair</span></div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>⚠ Miele residential vs Miele Professional — this page is residential only</h2>
    <p>Miele operates two distinct product lines with separate parts catalogs, service-technician certification programs, and distribution networks. <b>Miele residential</b> — the MasterCool built-in refrigerator line covered on this page, plus Miele residential dishwashers, washers, dryers, ovens, and cooktops sold through the residential dealer network to private households. <b>Miele Professional</b> — Miele's commercial division covering commercial dishwashers for foodservice (glass washers, utensil washers), healthcare washers (bedpan washers, instrument washers), commercial laundry for multi-unit residential and light commercial, and laboratory-grade cleaning equipment for clinical and research applications. The two product lines are manufactured in separate facilities, use separate OEM parts catalogs, and are serviced by separate factory-authorized technician networks.</p>
    <p>Our SDAR service scope is <b>Miele residential only</b>. If you're trying to service a Miele Professional unit (typical indicators: commercial capacity, multi-user access controls, installation in a restaurant / bar / clinical / dental / laboratory / laundromat setting), please reach out to Miele Professional's factory-authorized commercial service network rather than a residential appliance-repair company. See also our <a href="/brands/miele-professional-dishwasher-repair/">Miele Professional dishwasher repair</a> page for cross-track disambiguation awareness.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>MasterCool built-in column lineup we service</h2>
    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>F1411Vi + F2811Vi integrated freezer column</h3><p>24" + 30" integrated freezer column, panel-ready full-overlay. F2811Vi larger capacity; pairs with K-series refrigerator column.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>K1911Vi + K2802Vi + K2902Vi refrigerator column</h3><p>24" + 30" integrated refrigerator column. Pairs with F-series freezer for matched-column suite.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>KF 2981 Vi combination</h3><p>Combination refrigerator-freezer column in single cabinet. Panel-ready integrated. Compact matched-column alternative.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>KFN 9855 iDE legacy French-door</h3><p>Legacy French-door built-in from 2010s-era MasterCool generation. Still common in LA install base; parts supported.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>MasterCool app + home network</h3><p>Current generations integrate with MasterCool app via Miele@home network. Temperature monitoring + service alert + firmware update.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>European integration standard</h3><p>Full-overlay panel accepting custom cabinetmaker finishes. European design-direction kitchens + minimalist architectural custom.</p></div>
